description:
21:9, 1440p animated wallpaper of a fanart for FromSoft's Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice. Added godrays, lightshafts, falling leaves and dust motes, nothing else. The original artwork's colors were edited. :)                                          

Artwork by TacoSauceNinja @ Deviantart. Check it out [url=https://www.deviantart.com/tacosauceninja/art/Die-Twice-790690570]here.[/url]
title: Shadows Die Twice
